  array('post_name' => 'ruth-zabetta-takes-inspiration-from-the-buildings-of-new-york-city-for-her-latest-collection','post_title' => 'Ruth Zabetta Takes Inspiration from the Buildings of New York City for her Latest Collection','post_content' => 'Ruth Zabetta presented yet another collection at the New York Fashion Week for the Fall/Winter\'19 Showcasing with the help of CAAFD.  Zabetta’s<span style="font-weight: 400;"> collection is created for the modern but feminine woman and inspired by years of culture and design.</span>This collection was inspired by New York City and its buildings. She showcased a selection of elegant cocktail outfits and evening wear, where meticulous attention was given to tailoring. <span style="font-weight: 400;">The collection exhibits feminism, modern lines and unique cuts, creating beautiful silhouettes consistently though all the pieces</span>

