  array('post_name' => 'mansur-gavriel-present-a-minimalistic-collection-at-the-nyfw','post_title' => 'Mansur Gavriel present a  Minimalistic Collection at the NYFW','post_content' => 'Mansur Gaverial decided to show their New York Studio as they presented a minimalist see now, buy now Spring Summer Collection at the New York Fashion Week. The collection was bright, light and airy. The designer duo set up 12 models, in looks, in various tableau throughout the room to bring some freshness to the collection. People got to see the designs up close and personal and it added a personal touch to the whole show. The palette was mostly yellow and blue with some neutral shades thrown in the mix.
