  array('post_name' => 'school-daze-victor-glemaud-at-the-nyfw','post_title' => 'School Daze by Victor Glemaud at the NYFW','post_content' => 'Victor Glemaud\'s <a href="http://www.nyfw.events" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fall\'19</a> Collection got a wonderful joyous reaction from those present in his studio. Titled, "School Daze," the collection as described by Glemaud showed what people would like to wear after summer vacation. The range was all knit but showed diversity in techniques.

Portrait of trans actress Indy Moore hung around the Spring Studio where the designer presented his collection. Glemaud said he found an instant connection with Moore when he met her for the first time and really wanted to work with her for a while. Moore was seen having a gala time in and around the Lowell Hotel in Manhattan. Her portraits depicted a joyous, carefree Moore as she danced in Central Park. The collection showed one-pieces, cardigans, jackets, tops and jumpsuits in various materials and knits. "Fierce Fall Fashion," is what Glemaud called it.

<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-20696" src="https://www.ifashionnetwork.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/00001-VICTOR-GLEMAUD-NEW-YORK-FALL-19-CREDIT-RICHIE-SHAZAM.jpg" alt="" width="2732" height="4098" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-20697" src="https://www.ifashionnetwork.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/00004-VICTOR-GLEMAUD-NEW-YORK-FALL-19-CREDIT-RICHIE-SHAZAM.jpg" alt="" width="2732" height="4098" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-20698" src="https://www.ifashionnetwork.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/00005-VICTOR-GLEMAUD-NEW-YORK-FALL-19-CREDIT-RICHIE-SHAZAM.jpg" alt="" width="2732" height="4098" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-20699" src="https://www.ifashionnetwork.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/00006-VICTOR-GLEMAUD-NEW-YORK-FALL-19-CREDIT-RICHIE-SHAZAM.jpg" alt="" width="2732" height="4098" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-20700" src="https://www.ifashionnetwork.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/00007-VICTOR-GLEMAUD-NEW-YORK-FALL-19-CREDIT-RICHIE-SHAZAM.jpg" alt="" width="2732" height="4098" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-20701" src="https://www.ifashionnetwork.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/00009-VICTOR-GLEMAUD-NEW-YORK-FALL-19-CREDIT-RICHIE-SHAZAM.jpg" alt="" width="2732" height="4098" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-20702" src="https://www.ifashionnetwork.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/00010-VICTOR-GLEMAUD-NEW-YORK-FALL-19-CREDIT-RICHIE-SHAZAM.jpg" alt="" width="2732" height="4098" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-20703" src="https://www.ifashionnetwork.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/00011-VICTOR-GLEMAUD-NEW-YORK-FALL-19-CREDIT-RICHIE-SHAZAM.jpg" alt="" width="2732" height="4098" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-20704" src="https://www.ifashionnetwork.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/00012-VICTOR-GLEMAUD-NEW-YORK-FALL-19-CREDIT-RICHIE-SHAZAM.jpg" alt="" width="2732" height="4098" />

