  array('post_name' => 'billie-eilish-collaborates-with-hm','post_title' => 'Billie Eilish collaborates with H&M','post_content' => 'Billie Eilish collaborates with H&amp;M on their latest collaborative line that is made using sustainably sourced eco-friendly materials like organic cotton. In their latest merch line, the H&amp;M x Billie Eilish, H&amp;M mimics Billie Eilish\'s style from articles of clothing to accessories that are edgy and environmental at the same time.

[caption id="attachment_26926" align="alignnone" width="866"]<img class="wp-image-26926 size-full" src="https://ifashionnetwork.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Screen-Shot-2020-01-05-at-8.41.03-AM.png" alt="Billie Eilish collaborates with H&amp;M" width="866" height="1114" /> Image via H&amp;M[/caption]

This isn\'t Eilish\'s first collaboration. The 18-year old singer has collaborated with other fashion empires such as Urban Outfitters and Bershka after which Billie Eilish collaborates with H&amp;M in time for her stage tours.

The H&amp;M x Billie Eilish line was launched on the 2nd of January on H&amp;M\'s online sites and in stores. It includes a 16-piece line that features a printed sweatshirt dress, printed T-shirt dress, joggers, oversized sweatshirts, T-shirts, bucket hats, a bum bag, socks, and rib-knit hats. The pricing is affordable ranging from 5.99 dollars and going up to 34.99 for a hoodie.

[caption id="attachment_26927" align="alignnone" width="806"]<img class="wp-image-26927 size-full" src="https://ifashionnetwork.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Screen-Shot-2020-01-05-at-8.43.06-AM.png" alt="Billie Eilish collaborates with H&amp;M" width="806" height="1250" /> Image via H&amp;M[/caption]

H&amp;M had collaborated with Ariana Grande\'s Sweetener World Tour last and had found immense success. As its next move, H&amp;M has collaborated with American pop star Billie Eilish who\'s scheduled to perform about 50 live shows in 2020. Most of the venues have already been sold out, but for those who\'re lucky enough to have gotten a ticket, we know what they\'ll be wearing!

Billie Eilish\'s \'Where do we go\' tour kicks off on the 9th of March, 2020 from Miami, USA and ends on the 30th of July in London. Denzel Curry will accompany Billie Eilish on the The Where Do We Go? for all or portions of the tour.

&nbsp;','post_excerpt' => '','post_date' => '2020-01-06 04:43:44'),
  array('post_name' => 'kate-hudson-launches-new-eco-evening-collection','post_title' => 'Kate Hudson launches new Eco-Evening Collection','post_content' => '<span style="font-weight: 400;">American actress, author and fashion designer, Kate Hudson, known for her roles in movies such as How to Lose a Guy in 10 days, The Skeleton Key among others,  has added to her fashion empire by launching the new Nature Eco-evening collection. Kate Hudson launches new eco-evening collection amid friends and family. </span>

[caption id="" align="alignnone" width="421"]<a title="Kate Hudson" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/16891740@N00/5148398075/in/photolist-8QWTo4-6PER35-8QWThc-8QZYXE-8QWTi4-8QZZ4b-8QZZ69-8R1327-8QZYZh-7Ag5HA-5WpyuV-XeztAa-8k2DZn-wCaSiy-wmg8p9-5dhbu9-aAbw2c-9wrTht-9wuSPq-bCQNaW-6DphJ2-dQoMMG-9oF3iY-7YSaFi-7YVrYL-6fjZ1F-6fjYYF-6fjY6X-ba48hn-A6okLP-6htq9C-6hpf9g-6htq5Q-9D2Eev-9QByBC-cRJqEQ-25DfTt-55zbqr-HSGRL-7Kj8QP-5TvxvM-gCBugN-9HoZVC-6yTi1i-6pnyRy-6hpfmn-7kLvr6-6vkGsT-6hpfbM-d6oDWs" data-flickr-embed="true"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/4040/5148398075_f9792fc2e4_z.jpg" alt="Kate Hudson" width="421" height="640" /></a> via Flickr[/caption]

<span style="font-weight: 400;">As a perfect ensemble for the holiday season, the actress Kate Hudson launches new collection in Venice, California at the Butcher’s Daughter. The soiree was attended by big names that included Carson Meyer, Katherine McNamara, Shiva Rose, Jennifer Meyer among others. The cocktail party allowed the guests to browse through her collection while sipping on cocktails made from Kate’s vodka brand, King St. John. </span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;"> </span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">She hosted the event while wearing a jumpsuit from her own clothing collection. The floral-embroidered shimmering jumpsuit used jacquard fabric that was blended with recycled polyester. It was a stylish piece that was also environmental-friendly being that it was made from recycled polyester. </span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;"> </span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">The actress/ entrepreneur had launched her very first clothing line, </span><a href="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=74968X1525081&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.happyxnature.com%2F&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marieclaire.com%2Ffashion%2Fa27041030%2Fkate-hudson-happy-nature-fashion-line%2F%3Fpre%3Dfashion%252F%26prefix%3Da%26id%3D27041030%26del%3D%26variantId%3D%26post%3D%252Fkate-hudson-happy-nature-fashion-line"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Happy x Nature</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, which is pronounced Happy by nature. The line reflects her free-spirited and happy West Coast stylishness. The environmental-friendly clothing line consists of effortless pieces that reflect the actress’s nature.  The line focuses on effortless fashion and works on the brand’s mission for sustainability. </span>

&nbsp;','post_excerpt' => '','post_date' => '2020-01-06 04:50:31'),
  array('post_name' => 'sisters-launch-new-perfume-natalie-dylana-edp','post_title' => 'Sisters launch new perfume Natalie Dylana EDP','post_content' => '<span style="font-weight: 400;">Influencer sisters launch their new perfume and name it aptly after themselves. Natalie and Dylana Lim Suarez have launched their very first new perfume. Natalie Dylana is a beautiful fragrance that is an aromatic mixture of orange blossom, cedarwood, fig and jasmine petals. </span>

[caption id="" align="alignnone" width="799"]<a title="Sisters Suarez release a fragrance" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/186178552@N04/49310122963/in/photolist-2i8ngBR" data-flickr-embed="true"><img class="" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49310122963_992e8cb6fd_z.jpg" alt="Sisters Suarez release a fragrance" width="799" height="493" /></a> Sisters Suarez[/caption]

<span style="font-weight: 400;"> </span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Natalie and Dylana were born in Los Angeles and started their blogs on fashion in New York in the 2000s. Currently, they have about 850,000 followers on Instagram and are constantly in demand by brands such as Kate Spade, Olay and Rebecca Taylor. With the launch of their new perfume that they curated along with Scent Beauty, they plan to take their stardom to another level.   </span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">The Suarez Sisters Natalie Dylana Eau de Parfum has been described as </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">a multifaceted scent that is certain to flatter contrasts in all of us. It’s a perfume to appeal to our playful sides with juicy fig and mandarin, to our sensual side with orange blossom and jasmine petals and to our edgier sides with musk, amber woods, and cedarwood. The perfume has been designed to suit everyone and every mood that makes us who we are. </span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Natasha and Dylana, sisters launch new perfume,  aren’t the only ones that have been partnering with Scent beauty recently. The company had released a perfume ‘Cher Eau de Couture’ in November in partnership with Cher, a legendary singer, and performer. </span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;"> </span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">The 30ml bottle is available for sale for $50. </span>

&nbsp;','post_excerpt' => '','post_date' => '2020-01-06 04:54:21'),
  array('post_name' => 'barneys-shuts-online-operations-as-it-awaits-its-takeover','post_title' => 'Barneys shuts online operations as it awaits its takeover','post_content' => '<span style="font-weight: 400;">Barneys New York </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">has officially stopped offering its clearance stock on websites. Websites Barneys.com and Barneyswarehouse.com sites have been suspended and the retailer is now transferring remaining stock to its stores that are scheduled to close soon. These stores might be in operation until February 2020. However, </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Barneys New York’s Madison Avenue store in Manhattan will stay open for another year in a smaller form. Barneys shuts online operations and awaits its takeover. </span>

[caption id="" align="alignnone" width="858"]<a title="Barneys Exterior" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/urbanphotoz/16115235918/in/photolist-qy3Nc9-8N7oUR-T4c9FS-9GcviQ-MLajDs-GgCxgq-de26Yj-CdseYk-81AK5C-HUaou4-273F8Bx-81xzL8-EcWCvA-aYzr2z-9Gi5LE-5Hngon-n84xoR-iYWS88-aYzHkg-aYzmaB-iYXGbJ-aYzora-aYzRxZ-5HrzRE-aYztNZ-aYzNqg-fwnRyf-aYzUrK-aYzKLk-aYzC1D-aYzwAr-aYzzmM-Mb2zDX-aYzEFV-PKmW7i-E5Sfmu-2aRnQtm-2cd3Yqx-2dyCaLF-MavAvS-92mgWY-4H9K2a-hcpCDN-5Z17hv-qdPEWQ-5cU1gA-pCVxSV-qMSphf-de2yM9-bsFggZ" data-flickr-embed="true"><img class="" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/7503/16115235918_bb6c322be7_z.jpg" alt="Barneys Exterior" width="858" height="448" /></a> Via Flickr[/caption]

<span style="font-weight: 400;"> </span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Barneys filed for bankruptcy in August and soon started closing stores following the court’s approval to Authentic Brands Group LLC to buy it and as a result, Barneys shuts online operations.  Authentic Brands Group, in turn, plans to open and operate about 40 Barneys shops in Saks Fifth Avenue stores. Users who type in the previous Barneys domain names now see pages reading Barneys at Saks or Saks Off Fifth.</span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">In October, a bankruptcy court accepted the $271 million bid made by Authentic Brands group which is a licensing company and owns various brands such as Juicy Couture, Authentic Brands for Barneys’ intellectual property. The licensing company which owns Aéropostale, Juicy Couture, Aéropostale, Nine West and Sports Illustrated was the highest bidder. </span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Barneys was the very first to introduce brands such as Armani, Comme des Garcons, Alaia, Louboutin and Zegna, and its store on Madison Avenue was an attraction to shoppers and window-shoppers. </span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">However, Barneys shut online operations and filed for bankruptcy in 2019 and found itself sold for parts. It had filed for bankruptcy years ago in 1996 and had changed hands many times after. Founded by Barney Pressman, Barneys started operation as a men’s retailer, but after three generations </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">of family proprietorship, it advanced into an expensive and elite supplier of New York’s style.</span>','post_excerpt' => '','post_date' => '2020-01-06 04:57:35'),
  array('post_name' => 'top-5-most-seductive-perfumes-for-women-worth-buying','post_title' => 'Top 5 most seductive perfumes for women worth buying','post_content' => '<span style="font-weight: 400">A seductive perfume is literally a head-turner. It builds a certain mystique around the woman prompting everyone around her to ask, “Who is she? And why does she smell so good?”  Here’s our pick for the top 5 most seductive perfumes a woman can wear: </span>

&nbsp;
<ol>
 	<li>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400">   Alien by Thierry Mugler: </span></h3>
</li>
</ol>
<a title="Alien Perfume" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/nicola_s/29214445942/in/photolist-5ZtS1o-TUBSkd-AQWHMR-7teC1Q-dBfr7P-24EeFA4-EinQx-93k915-LvzEXQ-cQjYWE-nBstuG-amK6gG-oPAaRh-7QPUYx-ixTsM8-6e3vd2-LAxGdR-PzDNHV-6XSDW-7taED2-7taFdF-ffoKE2-QS3Xqc-a885VX-arc9KL-2fqiFcL-docWaX-2efU1cb-2h9Qqex-2fdjUeY-8QuLUQ-NXH8W-sFpW5W-an5U3W-fGGjMJ-fGpKme-fGpKuP-mRBBcK-bsdoaA-7RABoE-a33T3v-7hBKja-6wXgX8-25bnj88-2fHnfeQ-49RRT-6hfgpE-7RxmGx-W3AXx5-7RABus" data-flickr-embed="true"><img class="alignnone" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/8304/29214445942_51d4d15906_z.jpg" alt="Alien Perfume" width="543" height="813" /></a>

<span style="font-weight: 400">This perfume is mystical, rich and exotic and captures the seductress within us. This is an easy entry in our list of top 5 most seductive perfumes for women.  Created by Dominique Ropion and Lauren Bruyere in the year 2005, it comes in a mysteriously engraved and precious stone refillable bottle.  It’s an alluring smell that smells unique and distinctive. Base notes consist of warm white amber, woodsy middle notes and the top note consists of Indian Jasmine. And to top it off the iconic bottle can be endlessly refilled through refill bottles or at the Mugler source. Don’t take our word for it? Trust the word of more than 10,000 women who’ve left reviews for this gorgeous smelling perfume. Users have voted this perfume to be extremely long-lasting and having a very heavy sillage. </span>

&nbsp;
<ol start="2">
 	<li>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400">   Flowerbomb by Viktor &amp; Rolf: </span></h3>
</li>
</ol>
<a title="♥ |[‍ FLOWERBOMB ]]| ♥" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/sooomicom/7287786480/in/photolist-c6ZP23-BTpwBc-LePoUp-5LUzDK-54X5Ae-aNUWK6-aNT4NK-5u1DUs-8bw7a5-aEJ7cG-YQrW6w-6Vk6zQ-KpYYta-2exyuZX-5jwzuR-653P4Q-KpHTbC-KViPLq-2hfpiuV-LiLhno-4vqRd2-fjYbrU-KpHJLS-67AFSq-zTSb61-5LYMtu-2hLWzhF-P4wi8R-SbiHvC-6oFEbH-gTBFA2-t9ookV-KViMqy-8kg1i8-6Vg2gV-6Vg266-8Wo6Fy-29zfvda-6bMjDx-qY4JpT-L6NTfN-4VDFJP-9GVt7i-8Uekrs-6QK4PZ-cKf3a9-ejRmKM-nRnXAa-7DmELW-9GYn1h" data-flickr-embed="true"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/7102/7287786480_8207e5f380_z.jpg" alt="♥ |[‍ FLOWERBOMB ]]| ♥" width="640" height="427" /></a>

<span style="font-weight: 400">Flowerbomb by Viktor &amp; Rolf is one of the most iconic perfumes ever created.  Designed by Olivier Polge, Carlos Benaim and Domitille Berthier in 2005, the Flowerbomb, as the name suggests, is described as an explosion of floral sensations: an explosive bouquet of fresh and sweet notes. The top notes consist of fresh and sweet bergamot and green tea. The heart is floral with sweet and intensive Sambac jasmine, centifolia rose, Cattleya orchid and freesia. The dry down consists of musk and patchouli. The bottle itself designed in the shape of diamond-granate compliments this sophisticated and glamorous perfume. </span>

&nbsp;
<ol start="3">
 	<li>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400">     Viva La Juicy by Juicy Couture:</span></h3>
</li>
</ol>
<a title="Viva La Juicy" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/noura3/5375712735/in/photolist-DL7BuB-q7Zd9x-bRoSfn-7RMvRA-ayVG1t-9c2W7k-4Fq8kF-5zKB2w-2eCuLru-anmVR5-anj768-6pq8Se-7VAvwq-5JV4KC-6yHq8g-5hAi5q-imLrka-imLukh-9skcRp-9W5XjJ-5nJmVZ-bVLzvQ-5hvWYv-7qGwVh-9eAo37" data-flickr-embed="true"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/5123/5375712735_d6d4cc0d22_z.jpg" alt="Viva La Juicy" width="640" height="432" /></a>

<span style="font-weight: 400">Launched in 2008, this gorgeous gourmet floral fragrance is loved by many. It is packaged in a typical Juicy Couture bottle and wrapped in a delightful silk fuchsia ribbon. The perfume opens with wild berries and juicy mandarin. The heart is a floral blend of gardenia, honeysuckle, and jasmine. The dry down is a lovely mix of amber, caramel, sandalwood, vanilla, and pralines. Users define this perfume as having moderate longevity and moderate sillage. With the Viva La Juicy on your skin, you’re sure to become the life of the party. </span>

&nbsp;
<ol start="4">
 	<li>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400">   Lovely by Sarah Jessica Parker: </span></h3>
</li>
</ol>
<a title="lovely" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/pearled/4603996648/in/photolist-81QFNy-yfnwg-5CQU8W-4VS37c-RspVpd-VHS5jr-8Bj9GB-RuBPij-9rVTvP-8ei4uS-9rV48c-6QHjrt-6QMoBj-pbmVb-4LnDGG-7KTDLQ-9pThBn-fcQq6t-oRmSiE-9guAVc-6MNf3t-5uFLtG-7rmM19-2i7gtJJ-2gAnQhH-bA9hQH-nxvtgY-PG1Tp1-65HGZZ-8gLbh-QJ7dv8-ajun6f-73dWL2-rgZNGa-7mpTSJ-5caZdN-8RwoNj-6yP26w-9XFobZ-bDzcCX-5VKMDG-84xaif-crCJ4L-HFwDHt-atbssF-X8NuD-DejusU-6jrPyU-nzyyWA-cWgERN" data-flickr-embed="true"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/3300/4603996648_6db7dc0220_z.jpg" alt="lovely" width="640" height="427" /></a>

<span style="font-weight: 400">Lovely is the very first fragrance created by Sarah Jessica Parker, best known for her performance as Carrie Bradshaw on the HBO show Sex and the city. Lovely is described as a soft, discreet and intimate fragrance. The opening notes consist of citrus and rosewood with a hint of lavender. The heart of the perfume has a beautiful assortment of apple martini, narcissus, and orchid. The dry down is beautiful consisting of white amber, woody notes, white musk, and cedar. Created by Laurent Le Guernec and Clement Gavarry with Parker herself as the creative director, the perfume has been described as being appropriate for women of all generations. </span>

&nbsp;
<ol start="5">
 	<li>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400">   Black Opium by Yves Saint Laurent: a strong contender in the list of top 5 seductive perfumes for women: </span></h3>
</li>
</ol>
<a title="ysl-black-opium-2014-edie-campbell- 5" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/163941455@N05/41589148141/in/photolist-26n6fNi-22h7NSt-9UJqLz-atoRuV-bo5Nhe-6vPRu9-Rm9u2t-q2aLUq-qMM6UT-p5i7Ez-bX5ejV-23ydP2z-aKLzRt-82aPSp-e9t5Ng-qQet2Y-s21b4b-541uVA-M82siQ-8ki1NH-EmTULu-9dsPvL-bXHZdA-8Ew1c-poVeDx-JerKLb-5itkAe-6Pk8A6-hxo5To-251f4A8-JerKC5-brPPSF-dKJxRQ-diveb1-e9yKrC-pJGBJu-q1SbkD-7e6EwC-dNntVP-ZHAuQv-r7PKPA-d9S5N7-b6dio4-82dU1-chyRAN-2bpmH4r-pJDqFS-edCXLc-aFPqfD-2djaVfW" data-flickr-embed="true"><img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/874/41589148141_0ced7a32aa_z.jpg" alt="ysl-black-opium-2014-edie-campbell- 5" width="493" height="640" /></a>

<span style="font-weight: 400">What can you say about a perfume that already has such a seductive name? The Black Opium by Yves Saint Laurent is a power-packed perfume that is addictive, fascinating and seductive at the same time. Created by Nathalie Lorson, Marie Salamagne, Olivier Cresp, and Honorine Blanc, the perfume is characterized to be warm and spicy. Top notes consist of pink pepper, orange blossom, and pear, in the heart of the perfume lie notes of coffee, jasmine, almond and licorice, and the sweet dry down comprises of vanilla, patchouli, cedar, and cashmere wood. The perfume is loved by many women and is also an Allure Best of Beauty award winner. The updated version for the much-loved Opium, this perfume is long-lasting and has a heavy sillage. </span>

&nbsp;','post_excerpt' => '','post_date' => '2020-01-06 05:05:04'),
  array('post_name' => 'how-to-look-fashionably-classy-and-polished-at-all-times','post_title' => 'How to look fashionably classy and polished at all times','post_content' => 'Everyone likes to look classy and polished and give off an air of grandeur to everyone around them. Thankfully, looking sophisticated and fashionable at the same time isn’t a difficult task. Here are our top tips on how you can look polished and classy at all times.

&nbsp;

&nbsp;
<h3>1. Personal grooming:</h3>
It always starts with the little things that add up to a whole lot more. Make sure your manicures are on point. Stick with a neutral or very subtle nail paint color that will suit most outfits rather than getting a dark or a flamboyant color that is more likely to clash with what you\'re wearing. Nail colors such as white or beige or French nails look amazing and complement most outfits.

Wash your hair every 2-3 days and keep it natural looking and clean. Your hair is your crowning glory and greasy hair never makes an impression. Keep your hair color as close to your natural hair color so you don’t have to constantly recolor it which costs a lot of time and money. Also, spending 15 to 20 minutes grooming your hair every day will make a huge difference. After getting your hair done, ask the stylist to show you how you can achieve the style yourself at home. Learn how to make easy ponytails and buns so you can still look manageable on days when you\'re running low on time.
<h3>2. Makeup:</h3>
When it comes to makeup, less is always more. Try to stay away from full coverage foundations, bold eyes, bold lips, and bold contours unless it’s for a special occasion. Stick to light or medium coverage foundations for your day to day look. If you have blemishes, hide them with concealer rather than going all out with your foundation. Try and find a signature nude lip color that flatters your skin tone and you can wear daily on the go. Take good care of your skin. Cleanse, tone and moisturize every day. Good skin is the base for a no-makeup makeup look.<a id="Qev8ykahT_tW5gO6nF7OHQ" class="gie-single" style="color: #a7a7a7; text-decoration: none; font-weight: normal !important; border: none;" href="http://www.gettyimages.com/detail/918259712" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"></a>
<h3>3. Perfume.</h3>
A good perfume makes a world of a difference to how a lady presents herself. Try not to change your perfumes frequently. Everyone should have a signature perfume that best suits the chemistry of their bodies and adds to the overall look of the person. Look for subtle fragrances that smell heavenly and match your personality.
<h3>4. Accessories:</h3>
A rule for accessories is to go minimal with timeless pieces such as classic bags and jewelry. Don’t wear everything at once as it gives off a vibe that you’re trying too hard. Wearing a beautiful emerald earpiece? Ditch the bracelet. Keep it simple. Invest in classic bags and shoes since that is going to match countless numbers of outfits. A good bag and a good shoe can carry through hundreds of outfits and looks.

Another classic accessory for winter is a good neutral scarf. In summer, a cute necktie adds wonders to an outfit. Also, a pair of classic sunglasses will last you a long time and add to your overall polished look.
<h3>5. Wardrobe:</h3>
Stick to a color scheme. If you’re not sure where to start, neutrals are the way to go. Go with creams, whites, beiges and pale subtle pinks that make putting outfits so much easier. When you have a colorful wardrobe, you are required to buy more clothes to suit those colors. But if you have a color scheme, it’s so much easier to style a look.

Try mixing classic wardrobe staples with trendy pieces. For instance, wrap a necktie around the handle of your bag to make it look more trendy and pair it with a classic white trench coat. High necks look very chic in winter and blouses with clean lines and feminine details look great in summer.

A well-fitting outfit will look more put together than loose outfits. Take the time to research your body type to see what kind of clothes suit you the best and make purchases accordingly. Not all clothes are meant for every body type.

Never underestimate the power of a good tailor. A little expense towards tailoring your clothes to fit your body will make a huge difference in how you present yourself. Pair flowy tops with tight skirts or shorts and pair skater skirts with a tight top or a high neck top.

Make sure your clothes are ironed or steamed to keep it’s appearance presentable. Get the lint off a woolen sweater or coat with a fabric shaver. Get a sticky lint roller if you own a pet to get the fur off your clothes.
<h3>6. Feel confident:</h3>
It’s not only on the outside that matters but also how you feel on the inside. How you conduct yourself contributes to whether or not you look classy and polished. Stand tall. Keep your Chin high. Focus on getting a good Posture when you sit or stand. Keep your back straight and legs crossed when you sit. Being classy and polished is in the air you give off. You could be wearing all the right clothes and accessories and it wouldn’t matter if you didn’t feel confident in your own skin.

With a little effort, you can look polished and classy each day every day. Remember, Dressing well is a form of good manners. -Tom Ford.

